'''Katrin Kunde''' is a German artist. She has had several exhibitions of her paintings near her home in Dresden, Germany, as well as contributing artwork to [[Amon Hen (journal)|''Amon Hen'']] and [[Mallorn (journal)|''Mallorn'']].
